						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/05/09/tfttf635-interview-jon-miller-drones/" title="12:28 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-05-09T00:28:24+00:00">May 9, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/ravsitar/" title="View all posts by Ravsitar" rel="author">Ravsitar</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
