				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4793&amp;md5=ae4af4f37e5dc8c3111026ebea56b1a2" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><audio id="podlovewebplayer_1" style="width: auto; height: 30px" controls type="audio/mpeg" preload="none" src="http://www.podtrac.com/pts/redirect.mp3/media.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/tfttf635_jonmillerondrones.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" preload="none">
