	<article id="post-4603" class="post-4603 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-everesttrek category-specials category-tipsfromthetopfloor tag-everest-trek tag-jon-miller tag-special">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/01/11/tfttf621-special-brothers-and-mountains/" rel="bookmark">tfttf621 &#8211; Special: Brothers and Mountains</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/01/11/tfttf621-special-brothers-and-mountains/" title="9:15 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-01-11T21:15:23+00:00">January 11, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/ravsitar/" title="View all posts by Ravsitar" rel="author">Ravsitar</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
