				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2012/05/29/tfttf549-thelma-and-louise/" title="3:07 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-05-29T03:07:02+00:00">May 29, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/ravsitar/" title="View all posts by Ravsitar" rel="author">Ravsitar</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
